resources.string: The Option Is Updating on 31st July. We Provide All Sorts Of Possible Form Of Educational Platform For Teachers And Students In Portable Manner. So Be With Us. Thank You!

This Application is known as "Teacher-Student Interactive Platform", here teacher and student both can interact with each other from their remote location and also they can share the information regarding the education and others. In this application teacher and student together need to register themselves and even it is prime duty of teacher to guide his/her each and every student regarding the platform and its utility, which is not possible for the teacher to perform always. The main advantage of this platform is that, here both teacher and student can interact each other at anytime and from anywhere. This platform is not the end because we primarily launch our first version of this application for the implementation of education which is choked due to pandemic, we also ready for the second version of this application, as in our next update we provide those feature that we cannot provide right now during our app launching.\n This application is developed by: Krypto Developers Pvt. Ltd. (9706302163/7002858945)
